, when National Football League playerColin Kaepernick took a kneeduring the American national anthem as a public protest against systemic racism, the result was an onslaught of online hate.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999996257429, \"rank\": 3.739758262422624e-10, \"text\": \"National Football League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}, {\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Star-Spangled_Banner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"American national anthem\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Star-Spangled_Banner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Star-Spangled_Banner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kneeduring\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"a public protest\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"systemic racism\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"an onslaught\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"online hate\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The proliferation of social media use has enabledwide-ranging engagementinonline public shamingthat is aimed at humiliating, offending, denigrating andpunishing the targeted person.\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The proliferation\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"social media use\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"enabledwide-ranging engagementinonline public\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"shamingthat\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"offending\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"the targeted person\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For some, engaging in public online shaming serves to attract attention, provide a sense of importance andbuild a sense of identity.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public online shaming\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"serves\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"importance andbuild\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"identity\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Research evidence indicates that women and others from equity-denied groups are disproportionatelytargets of online shaming.\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Research evidence\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"equity-denied groups\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"disproportionatelytargets\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"online shaming\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, when X (formerly Twitter) accounts of athletes involved in the 2020 Tokyo Olympics were monitored prior to and during the Games,70 per cent of targeted athletes were women, with women receiving 87 per cent of the hateful messages directed at athletes.\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"formerly Twitter\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games,70\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram