n.\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3170, \"end\": 3178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999847729025241, \"rank\": 7.62288968535971e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 3185, \"end\": 3197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3219}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's welterweight division\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Italian boxer Angela Carini received several powerful blows from Khelif, she withdrew from the match after just 46 seconds.An online hostile and discriminatory discourse immediately arose.\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3264, \"end\": 3271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9997897800830666, \"rank\": 0.0001982818104064552, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3278, \"end\": 3291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several powerful blows\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3323}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3364}, {\"ngram\": 