, \"to\": 4844}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"sportification\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4867}, {\"ngram\": \"its inclusion\", \"from\": 4888, \"to\": 4901}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 4917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn's Paris performance was widely considered by media and social media users as bizarre because of her movement choices (most notably, kangaroo hops).\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 5073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4921, \"end\": 4925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9757526272794822, \"rank\": 0.02271532452605753, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 4928, \"end\": 4933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9997203794938444, \"rank\": 0.0002796987156730294, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4976}, {\"ngram\": \"social media users\", \"from\": 4981, \"to\": 4999}, {\"ngram\": \"her movement choices\", \"from\": 5022, \"to\": 5042}, {\"ngram\": \"kangaroo\", \"from\": 5058, \"to\": 5066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was accused of being well below the athletic standard expected at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 5075, \"to\": 5163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletic standard\", \"from\": 5111, \"to\": 5132}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some claimed she made a mockery of breakdancing, while others accused her of benefitting from white privilege, being a diversity hire andmanipulating the system to gain a spot at the Games, a conspiracy that was countered byan Australian fact-checking organization.\", \"from\": 5164, \"to\": 5429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5391, \"end\": 5401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9999495107262796, \"rank\": 5.0432462013900724e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mockery\", \"from\": 5186, \"to\": 5195}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5225}, {\"ngram\": \"white privilege\", \"from\": 5258, \"to\": 5273}, {\"ngram\": \"a diversity hire\", \"from\": 5281, \"to\": 5297}, {\"ngram\": \"the system\", \"from\": 5314, \"to\": 5324}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 5333, \"to\": 5339}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 5343, \"to\": 5352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn quickly became the subject of widespread online criticism and public shaming for her behavioural transgression, specifically for a performance that was perceived by many viewers as below the high skill level expected at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5431, \"end\": 5435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9757526272794822, \"rank\": 0.02271532452605753, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the subject\", \"from\": 5451, \"to\": 5462}, {\"ngram\": \"widespread online criticism\", \"from\": 5466, \"to\": 5493}, {\"ngram\": \"her behavioural transgression\", \"from\": 5517, \"to\": 5546}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance\", \"from\": 5565, \"to\": 5578}, {\"ngram\": \"many viewers\", \"from\": 5601, \"to\": 5613}, {\"ngram\": \"the high skill level\", \"from\": 5623, \"to\": 5643}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, many in the breaking community supported Gunn, noting that breaking is about self-expression and creativity, contrary to the masculine construction of performance success that is atthe root of sports in the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 5676, \"to\": 5906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5726, \"end\": 5730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9757526272794822, \"rank\": 0.02271532452605753, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the breaking community\", \"from\": 5693, \"to\": 5715}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 5744, \"to\": 5752}, {\"ngram\": \"self-expression\", \"from\": 5762, \"to\": 5777}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 5782, \"to\": 5792}, {\"ngram\": \"the masculine construction\", \"from\": 5806, \"to\": 5832}, {\"ngram\": \"performance success\", \"from\": 5836, \"to\": 5855}, {\"ngram\": \"atthe root\", \"from\": 5864, \"to\": 5874}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 5878, \"to\": 5884}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5888, \"to\": 5905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn's published work has cited concerns about how breakdancing's inclusion in the Olympics decontextualizes viewers from long cultural histories - for example of the music genres that influenced breaking and the creativity central to the dance form.\", \"from\": 5908, \"to\": 6158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5908, \"end\": 5912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9757526272794822, \"rank\": 0.02271532452605753, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 5940, \"to\": 5948}, {\"ngram\": \"how breakdancing's inclusion\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 5983}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5987, \"to\": 5999}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 6017, \"to\": 6024}, {\"ngram\": \"long cultural histories\", \"from\": 6030, \"to\": 6053}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 6060, \"to\": 6067}, {\"ngram\": \"the music genres\", \"from\": 6071, \"to\": 6087}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 6104, \"to\": 6112}, {\"ngram\": \"the creativity\", \"from\": 6117, \"to\": 6131}, {\"ngram\": \"the dance form\", \"from\": 6143, \"to\": 6157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her pre-Olympic insights and Olympic experiences raise questions about online critics who may have little or no understanding or knowledge of breaking and the ways in which their criticisms interact with gender-based violence to perpetuate perceptions of harmful norms and assumed norm transgressions.\", \"from\": 6160, \"to\": 6461, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her pre-Olympic insights\", \"from\": 6160, \"to\": 6184}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic experiences\", \"from\": 6189, \"to\": 6208}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6224}, {\"ngram\": \"online critics\", \"from\": 6231, \"to\": 6245}, {\"ngram\": \"little or no understanding\", \"from\": 6259, \"to\": 6285}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 6289, \"to\": 6298}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 6302, \"to\": 6310}, {\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 6315, \"to\": 6323}, {\"ngram\": \"their criticisms\", \"from\": 6333, \"to\": 6349}, {\"ngram\": \"gender-based violence\", \"from\": 6364, \"to\": 6385}, {\"ngram\": \"perceptions\", \"from\": 6400, \"to\": 6411}, {\"ngram\": \"harmful norms\", \"from\": 6415, \"to\": 6428}, {\"ngram\": \"norm transgressions\", \"from\": 6441, \"to\": 6460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In recognition of the evidence of potential harms experienced by those targeted by online hostility, theWorld DanceSport Federation offered psychological support to Gunn.\", \"from\": 6463, \"to\": 6633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6573, \"end\": 6583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dancesport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DanceSport\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dancesport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dancesport\"}, {\"begin\": 6628, \"end\": 6632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9757526272794822, \"rank\": 0.02271532452605753, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"recognition\", \"from\": 6466, \"to\": 6477}, {\"ngram\": \"the evidence\", \"from\": 6481, \"to\": 6493}, {\"ngram\": \"potential harms\", \"from\": 6497, \"to\": 6512}, {\"ngram\": \"online hostility\", \"from\": 6546, \"to\": 6562}, {\"ngram\": \"psychological support\", \"from\": 6603, \"to\": 6624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:We need far stronger support systems in the fight against gender-based violence These two cases highlight the shaming that can occur when behaviours run contrary to norms, especially for women.\", \"from\": 6635, \"to\": 6839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"far stronger support systems\", \"from\": 6653, \"to\": 6681}, {\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 6685, \"to\": 6694}, {\"ngram\": \"gender-based violence\", \"from\": 6703, \"to\": 6724}, {\"ngram\": \"These two cases\", \"from\": 6725, \"to\": 6740}, {\"ngram\": \"the shaming\", \"from\": 6751, \"to\": 6762}, {\"ngram\": \"behaviours\", \"from\": 6783, \"to\": 6793}, {\"ngram\": \"norms\", \"from\": 6810, \"to\": 6815}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6832, \"to\": 6837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also demonstrate the ways in which social media can be used bythose involved in sportas a platform to commit acts ofgender-based violenceand reinforce andshape context-specific norms.\", \"from\": 6841, \"to\": 7029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 6863, \"to\": 6871}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 6881, \"to\": 6893}, {\"ngram\": \"bythose\", \"from\": 6906, \"to\": 6913}, {\"ngram\": \"sportas\", \"from\": 6926, \"to\": 6933}, {\"ngram\": \"a platform\", \"from\": 6934, \"to\": 6944}, {\"ngram\": \"acts\", \"from\": 6955, \"to\": 6959}, {\"ngram\": \"andshape context-specific norms\", \"from\": 6997, \"to\": 7028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Specifically in the cases of Khelif and Gunn, norms were associated with appearance, physical prowess and skill level expected of women at the Olympic Games- one was accused of being too talented at her sport, while the other was accused of being sub-standard.\", \"from\": 7031, \"to\": 7291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7071, \"end\": 7075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9757526272794822, \"rank\": 0.02271532452605753, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cases\", \"from\": 7047, \"to\": 7056}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 7060, \"to\": 7066}, {\"ngram\": \"norms\", \"from\": 7077, \"to\": 7082}, {\"ngram\": \"appearance\", \"from\": 7104, \"to\": 7114}, {\"ngram\": \"physical prowess and skill level\", \"from\": 7116, \"to\": 7148}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 7161, \"to\": 7166}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games-\", \"from\": 7170, \"to\": 7188}, {\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 7230, \"to\": 7239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Preventing online public shaming is critical given the well-documented evidence of psychological, social and financial harms experienced by those targeted.\", \"from\": 7293, \"to\": 7448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"online public shaming\", \"from\": 7304, \"to\": 7325}, {\"ngram\": \"the well-documented evidence\", \"from\": 7344, \"to\": 7372}, {\"ngram\": \"psychological, social and financial harms\", \"from\": 7376, \"to\": 7417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To achieve more diverse and inclusive sport and dance environments, it is essential to prevent and appropriately respond to gender-based violence, including incidents of online public shaming.\", \"from\": 7449, \"to\": 7641, \"enti